com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance

Class ConcurrentOrderMgr

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance.ConcurrentOrderMgr

  • public class ConcurrentOrderMgr
extends Object
    ConcurrentOrderMgr is a utility class that keeps tracks of the number of concurrent bid and ask orders in a security by a client. This class uses the singleton pattern and does not maintain any persistent data for reasons of speed. It reconstructs state from the MarketMirror.
    Author:
    Tom Vasak TODO Make this a per ComplianceProcessor object, not a another bloody TODO singleton.
